title: ITV Tour De France 2011 Stage 12 Highlights (14th July 2011) PDT

ITV Tour De France 2011 Stage 12 Highlights (14th July 2011) PDTV x264 AAC

Gary Imlach, Chris Boardman and Ned Boulting present highlights of Stage 12, Cugnaux to Luz-Ardiden a 211km ride. They have reached the Pyrenees and today there are three major climbs including the Col du Tourmalet and a mountain top finish on Luz Ardiden. Commentary: Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen.
